Ro-Bot is a Shell script program [For Arch Linux based distros] 

Keep Scripts folder in your /home then give permission, run as sudo “chmod x+u ./Ro-Bot.sh“

Dialog package is required [pacman -Syu dialog]

  Some changes for 2.0 Version [Coming soon] 
  “echo“ command replaced by printf
  Support for “English language“
  Support for “Spanish language“
  Suport for Debian based distros
  “Others minor improvements“
